mixin dot
	span(class="dot") ·
mixin section(id, label)
	h2(class="hr", id=id)
		span.hr= label
doctype 5
html
	head
		meta(charset="utf-8")
		meta(http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible", content="IE=edge")
		title André Staltz
		meta(name="description", content="Holistic Web Developer")
		meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no")
		link(rel="stylesheet", href="/static/css/bootstrap.min.css")
		link(href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/3.2.1/css/font-awesome.min.css", rel="stylesheet")
		link(href="/static/css/main.css", rel="stylesheet")
		script(src="/static/js/modernizr-2.6.1.min.js")
	body
		.header
		.avatar
		.container
			.row
				div(class="col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3")
					.centered
						h2.name-title 
							a(href="#name", id="link-name-title", class="name-title", 
							data-toggle="tooltip", title="Real name?") 
								| André Staltz
						h3.name-subtitle HOLISTIC WEB DEVELOPER
					p
						span.syllables ho·lis·tic
						| Emphasizes the importance of the whole 
						| and the interdependence of its parts.
					+section('about-me', "ABOUT ME")
					p
						| Hi, I'm a web developer and designer. My passion is 
						| to build meaningful products out of my many wild ideas.
					p
						| I work as Software Engineer at 
						a(href="http://www.futurice.com", target="_blank") Futurice
						|. I'm the founder of 
						a(href="http://www.iroquote.com", target="_blank") Iroquote
						|, a platform for online discussion societies.
					p
						| I come from Brazil, but have no interest in football
						| and many other things that identify them. I'm rare.
						| Currently I live in Finland, where it's nice and cold.
					+section('find-me', "FIND ME")
					ul.horizontal
						li
							a(href="http://www.twitter.com/andrestaltz", class="twitter-bg")
								i.icon-twitter
						li
							a(href="http://www.facebook.com/andre.staltz", class="facebook-bg")
								i.icon-facebook
						li
							a(href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/andrestaltz", class="linkedin-bg")
								i.icon-linkedin
						li
							a(href="http://www.stackoverflow.com/users/315752/staltz", class="stackexchange-bg")
								i.icon-stackexchange
						li
							a(href="http://www.github.com/staltz", class="github-bg")
								i.icon-github
						li
							a(href="mailto:andrestaltz@gmail.com", class="email-bg")
								i.icon-envelope
					+section('extras', "EXTRAS")
					p
						| Sometimes I make games. With my friend 
						a(href="http://www.glauberkotaki.com", target="_blank") Glauber Kotaki
						|  I've made some under the label 
						a(href="http://www.glauberkotaki.com/zeroduo", target="_blank") ZeroDuo
						|, and by myself I've made 
						a(href="http://www.kongregate.com/games/STALTZ/rgblend", target="_blank") RGBlend
						|, a color puzzle game. I've also had an important role in a
						| community of brazilian game designers named 
						a(href="http://www.iroquote.com/gamebrain", target="_blank") Gamebrain
						|.
					p
						a(href="http://users.ics.aalto.fi/desoua1/", target="_blank") I'm MSc
						|  in Computer Science, and for my 
						a(href="http://users.ics.aalto.fi/desoua1/HAcid_Thesis.pdf", target="_blank") Master's Thesis
						|  I developed 
						a(href="https://bitbucket.org/staltz/hacid/wiki/Home", target="_blank") HAcid
						|, a Java client library that enables ACID transactions on 
						a(href="http://hbase.apache.org/", target="_blank") HBase
						|. In Brazil I graduated BSc in Computational Mathematics at 
						a(href="https://www.ufmg.br/english/", target="_blank") UFMG
						|, where I got to do research on Computational Fluid Dynamics and also
						a(href="http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1571065310000041", target="_blank") Operations Research
						|.
					p
						| I have a 
						a(href="http://staltz.blogspot.com", target="_blank") blog
						|, where I occasionally write about programming and softwares.
						| I also write at 
						a(href="http://medium.com/@andrestaltz", target="_blank") Medium
						|  about life.
					p
						| I'm an acoustic guitarrist and a composer. I listen to different
						| genres, but mostly instrumental music. Check out my 
						a(href="http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL24A51E95B3F5E4D2", target="_blank") acoustic songs recorded on video
						|. In 2004-2006 I recorded a progressive alternative rock/metal
						| album called 
						a(href="https://soundcloud.com/andrestaltz/sets/o-vazio-tem-um-nome", target="_blank")
							em O vazio tem um nome
						|.
						| You can find other compositions at 
						a(href="http://soundcloud.com/andrestaltz", target="_blank") Soundcloud
						|.
					+section('name', "MY NAME")
					p
						| <em>Staltz</em> is just a nickname I use on the web since 2004. My real
						| name is <strong>André Medeiros</strong>, but I try to avoid it 
						| because it's 
						a(href="https://www.google.com/search?q=andré+medeiros", target="_blank") disappointingly unoriginal
						|.
		.footer
			.container
				.row
					div(class="col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3")
						p Built with
						p
							a(href="http://www.python.org/", target="_blank") Python 2.7.4
							+dot 
							a(href="http://flask.pocoo.org/", target="_blank") Flask 0.10
							+dot
							a(href="http://gunicorn.org/", target="_blank") gunicorn
							+dot
							a(href="http://www.heroku.com", target="_blank") Heroku
							br
							a(href="https://github.com/SyrusAkbary/pyjade", target="_blank") pyjade
							+dot
							a(href="http://getbootstrap.com", target="_blank") Bootstrap 3
							+dot
							a(href="http://fontawesome.io", target="_blank") FontAwesome 3.2.1
						p
							a(href="https://github.com/staltz/staltzpage", target="_blank") Source code
